## Title
Chicago Pizza Oven Grinder

## Recommendation Summary

### Intent Assessment
A Chicago-style pizza pot pie baked in a bowl, inspired by the famous Chicago Pizza and Oven Grinder Co. restaurant. Stub with no ingredients or instructions.

### Categorization Changes
- **PARA**: "resources" → "07-resources" (Correct as reference recipe material.)
- **TREE**: "eat-drink-merriment/meals" → "eat-drink-merriment/meals/dinner" (Could be more specific under meals/dinner since this is a hearty dinner entree.)
- **GRAPH**: "links to Recipes - Meals, Food & Nutrition List" → "Add link to Pizza Dough (complementary recipe), Food Sourcing (cheese/protein sourcing)" (This recipe requires pizza dough. Food sourcing helps find quality mozzarella and sausage.)

